## piinstaller error

'''
in _get_const_info    argval = const_list[const_index] IndexError: tuple index out of range
'''

This is a Python 3.10 issue. To fix it: You have to go to the folder "Python310\Lib" and edit the file 'dis.py'. In the 'dis.py' file you have to find this "def _unpack_opargs" and inside the else statement write a new line with this: "extended_arg = 0", then save the file.

I did something like that:

else:
    arg = None
    extended_arg = 0 
yield (i, op, arg)


## possiamo provare NUTIKA

nutika è un compiler che possiamo usare per generare il file exe




python -m nuitka --follow-imports --onefile --include-package=trocr --include-distribution-metadata=torchaudio --windows-icon-from-ico=C:\Users\degreg0000\Desktop\work_in_progres\trascribre_assistant\assets\new_icon\predict\icon.png predict_als.py

--disable-console


